reviewText:
Girls of the Pac 10 is fifty-six minutes long and was released on video in 1994. The video was filmed in black and white and in color. Eleven ladies are in this video and five of them are not given that student ID card so they are not named. Also a segment from Sorority Lingerie Party is in this video. Are the ladies are beautiful to look at, but the camera operator does not do a lot of full nudity scenes. This is one video you might want to transfer to DVD. Girls of the Pac 10 get an AAA+++.

Terry - Arizona State - Major: Business Administration: Terry is working out on a stair master and becomes topless while still working out on the stair master. Slowly the boxer short comes off and she work out in the nude.

Rachel - Oregon - Major: Sports Medicine: Rachel becomes topless in front of a mirror and a few seconds later the panties are gone.

Andrea - University of California, Los Angeles - Major: Dance: Andrea is wearing a long white dress and become topless; a few seconds she is nude with the exceptions of the thigh high white stockings.

Leslie - University of Southern California - Major: English: Leslie starts off wearing blue jeans and a tee shirt. She becomes fully nude in a matter of seconds.

Tami - University of Arizona - Major: Business Administration: Tami is wearing a white robe and red lingerie by the fireplace and becomes topless. About a moment later she is fully nude.

Melissa - Major: Computer Science: Melissa looks like she is wearing a white ballerina outfit. Slowly she undresses to become half nude.

Christian - Stanford University - Major: Art History: Christian is outdoors and drinking a glass of wine. We never get to see her fully nude, though she does show some skin.

Kortne - Oregon - Major: Archaeology: She gets nude in a whirlpool.

Melissa - University of California, Los Angeles - Major: Criminology: She is topless very fast and about halfway into the segment she is nude.

Anthani - University of Southern California - Major: Communications: She becomes naked in front of a computer.

Jamie - International Studies: She is wearing purple lingerie and is talking on the phone. She gets nude towards the middle of the segment.
